<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Are you interested in the function of the nervous system in animals and humans? The Neuroscience minor allows students who are unable to major in Neurobiology, Physiology, &amp; Behavior to learn about the importance of the nervous system.</p>
